                 &kinds=<%=dto.getProduct_Kinds()%>&price=<%=dto.getProduct_Price()%>&stock=<%=dto.getProduct_Stock()%>', '상품 수정하기', 'width=450,height=200,location=no,status=no');">수정하기</Button></td>
